## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="a679f-104">该方法必须为 static 和 public。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a679f-104">The method must be static and public.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a679f-105">它必须返回 WMI 类的所有实例的集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a679f-105">It must return a collection of all instances of the WMI class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a679f-106">集合可以是任何类型可转换为<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a679f-106">The collection can be of any type convertible to <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="a679f-107">下面的示例演示如何使用枚举器属性来标记用于枚举类的实例的方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a679f-107">The following example shows how to use the Enumerator attribute to mark a method that is used to enumerate instances of a class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a679f-108">在这种情况下，Enumerate 方法使用<xref:System.Diagnostics.Process>类来检索所有计算机上运行的进程。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a679f-108">In this case, the Enumerate method uses the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Process> class to retrieve all of the processes running on the computer.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
[ManagementEnumerator]  
public static IEnumerable Enumerate()  
{  
   Process[] rgProcesses = Process.GetProcesses();  
   for (int i = 0; i < rgProcesses.Length; i++)  
   {  
      yield return new ProcessProvider(rgProcesses[i]);  
   }  
}  
```
